Kalphite workers work for the Kalphite Queen. They are found throughout the Kalphite Hive. They cannot poison, unlike the majority of Kalphites. They will spawn from cocoons to protect the Queen from intruders if she is close enough to one of them.

They are the weakest type of regular attackable kalphite. They can be killed for a kalphite Slayer assignment, and are ideal for lower level players.

Trivia[edit | edit source]

  • Kalphite workers spawned from the Queen are always aggressive towards players of any level.
  • If a Kalphite worker is spawned during the fight with the Kalphite Queen, they will experience a stretching glitch until the spawning animation finishes.
  • There are two pull-along kalphite toys resembling miniature Kalphite Workers on display at Azibo's Toy Store, but they cannot be bought.
